data.description: Gorgeously spacious 3 Bedroom / 2 Bath Pool home comes with a front porch. Home has an open floor plan with vaulted ceilings, tile, laminate and concrete flooring, and spacious bedrooms. Dining room off of the living rm/kitchen area. Also there is a built-in ofc/den area. Both bathrooms have combo tub/showers. Sellers have replaced both the Air conditioner systems and the water filtration system since their purchase. Large driveway and a 2 car garage gives you ample parking. Home has a large back yard with privacy fence. The inground pool is beautiful and enticing, both the pool area and extended lanai areas are screened/caged.
